{
  "description": "A black and white photograph captures a windswept coastal landscape. The foreground is dominated by a sandy beach gradually rising into undulating dunes covered in dense, scrubby vegetation. The dunes create a rolling horizon line, their textures emphasizing the erosive power of the wind. Above, a dramatic, swirling sky filled with dark, ominous clouds occupies the majority of the frame. The clouds are streaked and layered, creating a sense of depth and movement. The high contrast emphasizes the starkness of the scene. A few small trees are visible within the dunes. The composition draws the eye from the sandy foreground, up the dunes, and into the turbulent sky.",
